## ğŸš€ PR Workflow

### Create PR
```bash
git checkout -b feature/issue-X
# ...  code ... 
git push origin feature/issue-X
# Create PR on GitHub
```

### PR Template
```markdown
Closes #X

## Changes
- Item 1
- Item 2

## Testing
- [x] Tests passing
- [x] No console errors
```

